c-Trainer-Professional-6-1.webp 1128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" /><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-8709 size-large\" src=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PT-Academic-Trainer-Professional-7-1024x626.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1020\" height=\"624\" srcset=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PT-Academic-Trainer-Professional-7-1024x626.webp 1024w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PT-Academic-Trainer-Professional-7-300x183.webp 300w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PT-Academic-Trainer-Professional-7.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" /></p>\n", "featured_media": 8688, "segments": ["giang-vien-pte-magic-dat-chung-nhan-trainer-pearson"]}